       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1">Method of treating hyperglycemia
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p> Disclosed herein are methods for treating conditions and/or disorders
     related to hyperglycemia. Such conditions and/or disorders related to
     hyperglycemia include, but are not limited to, type I, II diabetes
     mellitus, gestational diabetes, other forms diabetes, and disorders
     related thereto. In particular, the present invention relates to methods
     of using (R)-(+)<B><I>-verapamil</I></B> or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt thereof
     in the treatment of conditions and/or disorders related to hyperglycemia.
</p>
       <HR>
